N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 363.1 - Definitions

State Regulations

For the purposes of this Part, the following terms shall have
the following meanings, unless the context clearly indicates otherwise: (a) Committee means the Soil and Water

Conservation Committee of the State of New York. (b) Department means the Department of

Agriculture and Markets of the State of New York. (c) District means a soil and water
conservation district in the State of New York. Notes
